des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Rosewill products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Rosewill" app in Android or IOS app market;
(2) Register one Rosewill Smart account in our "Rosewill" app;
(3) You need to have some Rosewill Smart devices in hand;
(4) Configure these devices in our Rosewill app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Rosewill" skill;
(5) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, IOS or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7) Search "Rosewill" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8) Click Enable skill of "Rosewill", and you'll be navigated to Rosewill login page;
(9) Input your Rosewill app account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10) Now all setup is finished. 
* Alexa, turn ZELo on 
* Alex, dim ZELo up 
* Alexa, dim ZELo down 
* Alexa, make ZELo cooler 
* Alexa, make ZELo warmer 
* Alexa, turn ZELo off
